snippet.title: Victoria II: Heart of Darkness Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Pre-Order now and receive some royal bonus-content: http://www.victoria2.com/game-info/buy-the-game

Read the Developer Diaries here:  http://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/content.php?113-development-diaries

Are you prepared to look into the Heart of Darkness? We're giving the world its first glimpse of what lies within the souls of greedy colonialists in the newest Victoria II expansion with a new trailer! Scramble for control of Africa in Paradox's upcoming release.
